game.name: Void Call
game.desc: They said, \"This is your last chance.\" I didn't care. The prototype R0-Z -- the first working time machine -- fell to MAGNUM CA, a space paramilitary at odds with my employer. My job is to steal it; my mission is my own. I'm done being their pawn. I won't let them keep it, and I won't use it. I'll let the void take it.
